{"tid":1466800,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[人手置頂]唔好灰心！仲有機會！我地仲有文宣，一定要入黎睇","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:55:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T18:25:25.000Z","uid":117600,"like":47,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"6a12024b82cebf38149ae772e32111a58a591802","tid":1466800,"uid":117600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:55:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">頭先開錯台，再開過</span><br />\n大家唔好灰心，我地而家更加要冷靜，同諗下一步點做。<br />\n<br />\n個人建議：<br />\n1. 一定要道歉<br />\n我地聽朝(愈早愈好）<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要為今日事件負責，道歉</span></span>，希望可以有民間記者會。始終今日影響左好多外國遊客+中立派，同埋鏡頭畫面一啲都唔好睇，我地無可厚非都要道歉先。（就算搞唔成記者會，希望都可以出篇文，大家一齊share）<br />\n<br />\n2. 未來文宣方向<br />\n2.1 強調時間性<br />\n我地一定要強調兩個月嘅無人回應+警察暴力，我地曾經有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兩個月嘅和平示威</span></span>，我地先被逼，別無他法升級，做出各種過份行為。<br />\n<br />\n2.2 承認過份行為<br />\n我地的確有做過呢啲擾民行為，但實屬被政府+黑警所逼，係佢地將我地變成惡魔，我地要將焦點變成，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點解我地變左惡魔</span></span>，令社會各屆明白。<br />\n<br />\n呢啲係我目前諗到嘅解決辦法，希望民間記者會籌委睇到。如果認同，可唔可以幫手推同分享。"},{"pid":"3d8df35da5b6f91a86e2b6036b4e8efab067696e","tid":1466800,"uid":117600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:58:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f14ba55c835394ae2c8a9978696328edf8fc06b9","tid":1466800,"uid":117600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:59:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ada362a6c14714a6495ebd9047bb346c8afe731","tid":1466800,"uid":219277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:59:54.000Z","msg":"［文宣方向／準備］狗改不了吃屎，今晚機場又係福建幫ｘ黑狗ｘ公安，破壞機場和理非！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dDKHuS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dDKHuS</a><br />\n<br />\n鍵盤戰士全面進場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dDLqnS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dDLqnS</a><br />\n<br />\n［有片］手 足 為 咗 救 人 先 打 狗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dDJLCS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dDJLCS</a><br />\n[正視聽]黑警舉真槍前因後果<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1465260\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1465260</a>"},{"pid":"9921b3e90316ad1b6b103239b1dc3b119455d9eb","tid":1466800,"uid":117600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:00:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"090bcf3b9c4de34b0de8fc2422971ee11628eae4","tid":1466800,"uid":117600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:01:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"09c54e2ec38ce8ce45680b2d50803def8184ccc6","tid":1466800,"uid":305023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:03:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bbaa87798d88638075fa703b71f96ab49be20647","tid":1466800,"uid":117600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:04:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c007e3cca7d583a959e07697072c8fcdb657fdcc","tid":1466800,"uid":117600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:07:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5349551bc220ec3ec47ac5d72be7cbbb13984df","tid":1466800,"uid":117600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:09:16.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"407fd24584ff6efa88ac0776219689c43a2c16ab","tid":1466800,"uid":117600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:09:26.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f7c6a9aaf646f5b5c5cb5a33f64b97c420b4274","tid":1466800,"uid":137459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:09:39.000Z","msg":"《警世》咪撚再捉戰犯啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466900\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466900</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9a17aa8684d0726a94451c87f758739230f0385d","tid":1466800,"uid":112241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:24.000Z","msg":"推，前線勇武，冷氣軍師必須撐"},{"pid":"cbd1d767ed17b3bd18b8f105fa9f4e84d