},{"pid":"4f844a17cee3e3fe294c95bae2d974bb7e5c653c","tid":1466800,"uid":12283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:22:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb161f2de57da7dc4b9dcdcc0732d31a0dfa6875","tid":1466800,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:23:05.000Z","msg":"要文宣谷818人數, 再係咁磨爛蓆會磨死自己<br />\n<br />\n呢個moment抽離一下冷靜一下唔好俾仇恨情緒同失敗主義支配自己"},{"pid":"bcb2bae4574a6bbc975ab26fa880b93cda4c5909","tid":1466800,"uid":143718,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:23:26.000Z","msg":"矯枉必須過正<br />\n可唔可以喺民記度講明唔再做任何不合作運動，<br />\n如果做 必定係立左死線之後再做。"},{"pid":"6045edaf777536bb2c1e8f89e405854e4e73c0dc","tid":1466800,"uid":151535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:23:59.000Z","msg":"文宣加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家對唔對得住天琦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466733\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466733</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不要被仇恨支配自己</span></span>"},{"pid":"da3863ea141add13e842ee1f91f68beaeeacfc89","tid":1466800,"uid":36088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:24:31.000Z","msg":"「唔完美，可接受，但需要改善、改進。」"},{"pid":"a861cf464a1ff9ad528eeec4d0bfb3da59201771","tid":1466800,"uid":117600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:24:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c629dee79f4bdd07c030aa2e7f21b780e92b1d4","tid":1466800,"uid":117600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:26:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"64d36f04760782934a21278bfc0dea6717da8666","tid":1466800,"uid":79704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:26:03.000Z","msg":"大家去講句 sorry<br />\n呢個記者其實幫我地解釋緊點解大家咁燥, 係因為811臥底事件<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RichScotford5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRichScotford5%2F&d=kDoZHsh44GLEl9RERzeBg2rU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=4b119a80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RichScotford5/</a><br />\n<br />\n大家幫手整個list, 仲有冇其他記者page去講對唔住, especially 如果頭先打到佢"},{"pid":"8671c7bfd75a19a1fc8da5e8dcaa1f32e73337dc","tid":1466800,"uid":287256,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:26:26.000Z","msg":"無論點都好，唔係話前線咁做係一定錯，但有衝動係事實！有錯咪認囉，唔認又點更進一步呢！<br />\n最緊要學好，下一次再做好啲！<br />\n前路仲有好長，唔好傷和氣，勇武有勇武既好，和利非亦有佢既優點，今次既事，有好多野可以改善，網絡上既溝通漏洞，處理懷疑係鬼既方法，火遮眼時對待記者救護既行為，唔啱唔係就咁就完左，改到啱，改到大家都認同，繼續去為5大訴求尼個目標進發！<br />\n香港人，加油！"},{"pid":"f739fbadf8f2f380381638719425e9f1092d8834","tid":1466800,"uid":81008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:26:55.000Z","msg":"再做好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"414c04a5baa4840a6be619f894e53227d76319e5","tid":1466800,"uid":117600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:27:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"545bd697b50e4eca8016405f3baa9fb66b15933a","tid":1466800,"uid":201816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:27:44.000Z","msg":"未輸㗎香港人<br />\n唔好咁快灰呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ef714cbdb118add1a2a4961af3283b107376593","tid":1466800,"uid":44906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:27:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dbb4d05be8db9404abbc4c3eb3c7d10d3befcd62","tid":1466800,"uid":117600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:28:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a8b34cdc3d335a17bfb37c17e14092536639422","tid":1466800,"uid":117600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:29:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9273ce57ef862c81cce52f3cd4399f76adde97b7","tid":1466800,"uid":69314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:29:49.000Z","msg":"請手足幫手推<br />\n<br />\n[置頂] 和理飛814<br />\n<a href=\"https://